          },
          "TITLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Neutron yields and emission rates of 50 MeV/U 18-O-ion",
                "on thick Be, Cu and Au targets."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "AUTHOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "Guisheng Li",
                "Tianmei Zhang",
                "Zongwei Li",
                "Youwu Su",
                "Shumin Zhang"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INSTITUTE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "3CPRIMP"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "REFERENCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "code": "J,NIM/A,404,349,1998",
                "code_unit": [
                  {
                    "unit": "J,NIM/A,404,349,1998",
                    "doi": "10.1016/S0168-9002(97)01104-2",
                    "field": {
                      "reference_type": "J",
                      "reference": {
                        "code": "NIM/A",
                        "number": null,
                        "volume": "404",
                        "part": null,
                        "issue": null,
                        "page": "349"
                      },
                      "date": 1998
                    }
                  }
                ],
                "unit_combination": "(%)"
              },
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "- By authors.",
                "1. The total neutron yield and neutron emission rate",
                "depend upon the atomic number of the target nucleus,",
                "that of lighter targets are greater than that of",
                "heavier targets when the incident ion energies per",
                "nucleon are identical.",
                "2. While using two different ions with identical energy",
                "per nucleon, e.g. 50 MeV/U 12-C and 18-O, to bombard",
                "the same target, the total neutron yield of 18-O ion",
                "greater than that of 12-C.",
                "3. In the three reaction studied, 18-O and 9-Be are",
                "neutron-rich nuclei and the excitation energy of result",
                "nucleus produced by 18-O+Be is greater markedly than",
                "that produced by 18-O+Cu and 18-O+Au.",
                "4. The variation regulation of neutron emission rates",
                "in the forward direction 2*pi solid-angle are similar",
                "to that of neutron yield."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "FACILITY": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "facility": [
                  "ACCEL"
                ],
                "institute": "3CPRIMP"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The experiment was carried out",
                "at HIRFL."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "THRES"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "",
                "Used threshold detectors to be:",
                "1.  High purity Al.  REACTION 13-AL-27(N,A)11-NA-24.",
                "Threshold energy - 7 MeV",
                "2.  Teflon.  Reaction 9-F-19(N,2N)9-F-18 . Threshold",
                "energy - 11 MeV;",
                "3.  Polythene.  Reaction 6-C-12(N,2N)6-C-11 . Threshold",
                "energy -20 MeV;",
                "4.  High purity Al. Reaction 13-AL-27(N,4P6N)9-F-18 .",
                "Threshold energy - 50 MeV."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "HPGE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " For measurement the activities of irradiated",
                "samples.  The efficiency of the system  was  calibrated",
                "using a standard 152-Eu gamma-source."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The thickness of Be, Cl, Au targets are greater than",
                "the ranges of the 18-O-ions."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SITA"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "BCINT"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "EXTB"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " A 50 MeV/U 18-O-ion beam passes through a hole",
                "in a concrete shielding wall and a deflecting magnet.",
                "Then through a pair of quadrupole lenses and a",
                "collimating slit into a experimental chamber."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "HISTORY": [
